<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover, maximum-scale=5.0">
<title>Travel Healthcare Licensing Hub — Reciprocity, Compact & Endorsement Guides (2026)</title>
<meta name="description" content="Traveler-first licensing hub: compare reciprocity, compact status, endorsement fees, and processing timelines for {{ deployed_count }} healthcare professions across all 50 states and DC.">
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ domain }}/">
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">
<meta property="og:title" content="Travel Healthcare Licensing Hub — Reciprocity, Compact & Endorsement Guides (2026)">
<meta property="og:description" content="Traveler-first licensing intelligence for healthcare clinicians moving state to state.">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ domain }}/">
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Serif+4:opsz,wght@8..60,400;8..60,600&family=Karla:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #ffffff;
  --paper: #faf9f7;
  --text: #222222;
  --muted: #666666;
  --line: #e5e1db;
  --link: #1a5f7a;
  --focus: rgba(26, 95, 122, 0.2);
  --badge-active-bg: #e6f4e8;
  --badge-active-txt: #2f7a3b;
  --badge-enacted-bg: #fff3e3;
  --badge-enacted-txt: #9a5b12;
  --badge-none-bg: #f0f0f0;
  --badge-none-txt: #777777;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-padding-top: 110px; }
body {
  margin: 0;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'Karla', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.65;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
button { font: inherit; border: 0; background: none; cursor: pointer; }
ul { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
h1, h2, h3, .stat-value {
  font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin: 0;
  color: #191919;
}
a:focus-visible, button:focus-visible, input:focus-visible {
  outline: 0;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--focus);
}

.site-nav {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  height: 48px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}
.site-nav-inner {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 920px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
.site-nav-brand {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #555;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.site-nav-links {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 20px;
}
.site-nav-links a {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #888;
}
.site-nav-links a:hover { color: #333; }

.hero-wrapper {
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 48px 24px 24px;
}
.hero-wrapper h1 {
  font-size: clamp(30px, 4.8vw, 44px);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: 17px;
  color: #444;
  margin: 0;
}

.stats-container {
  margin-top: 24px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: stretch;
  gap: 16px;
  background: var(--paper);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 16px;
}
.stat {
  min-width: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.stat-value {
  font-size: 26px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
}
.stat-label {
  margin-top: 4px;
  font-size: 12px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: #666;
}
.stat-divider {
  width: 1px;
  background: var(--line);
}

.search-wrap {
  max-width: 920px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 16px;
}
.search-inner {
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: #fff;
  padding: 12px;
}
.search-field {
  min-width: 0;
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}
.search-icon {
  position: absolute;
  left: 12px;
  color: #999;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.search-input {
  width: 100%;
  height: 40px;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 0 38px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-family: inherit;
  color: var(--text);
  background: #fff;
}
.search-input::placeholder { color: #999; }
.search-clear {
  position: absolute;
  right: 9px;
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  display: none;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 999px;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  color: #999;
  background: #fff;
}

.content {
  max-width: 920px;
  margin: 26px auto 0;
  padding: 0 16px 56px;
}
.grid-title {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #777;
  margin: 0 0 8px;
}

.profession-grid {
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: #fff;
}
.profession-card {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 48px minmax(0, 1fr) auto 20px;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 14px 12px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.profession-card:first-child { border-top: 0; }
.profession-card:hover { background: var(--paper); }

.card-icon {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: var(--paper);
  color: #444;
}
.card-icon svg {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
}
.card-body {
  min-width: 0;
}
.card-title {
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0;
}
.card-credential {
  margin: 2px 0 0;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #555;
}
.card-exam {
  margin: 3px 0 0;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #777;
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
}
.compact-badge {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 600;
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.compact-badge.active {
  background: var(--badge-active-bg);
  color: var(--badge-active-txt);
}
.compact-badge.enacted {
  background: var(--badge-enacted-bg);
  color: var(--badge-enacted-txt);
}
.compact-badge.none {
  background: var(--badge-none-bg);
  color: var(--badge-none-txt);
}
.card-chevron {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  color: #9a9a9a;
}

.empty-state {
  display: none;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: var(--paper);
  padding: 32px 20px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 12px;
}
.empty-state h3 { font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 6px; }
.empty-state p { margin: 0; color: #666; }

.features {
  margin-top: 36px;
  display: grid;
  gap: 12px;
}
.feature-card {
  background: var(--paper);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 18px;
}
.feature-card h3 {
  font-size: 20px;
  margin: 0 0 6px;
}
.feature-card p {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: #555;
}

.foot-wrapper {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding: 32px 16px 40px;
}
.foot {
  max-width: 920px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
  gap: 28px;
}
.foot h2 {
  font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  margin: 0 0 8px;
}
.foot p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #666;
  margin: 0;
}
.foot-links { display: grid; gap: 8px; }
.foot-links a {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--link);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-decoration-color: rgba(26, 95, 122, 0.3);
}
.foot-meta {
  display: block;
  margin-top: 12px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #999;
}

@media (max-width: 760px) {
  .site-nav-links { display: none; }
  .hero-wrapper { padding: 36px 16px 20px; }
  .stats-container {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .stat-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
  }
  .profession-card {
    grid-template-columns: 40px minmax(0, 1fr) 20px;
    grid-template-areas:
      "icon body chevron"
      "icon badge chevron";
    gap: 8px 10px;
  }
  .card-icon { grid-area: icon; }
  .card-body { grid-area: body; }
  .compact-badge {
    grid-area: badge;
    justify-self: start;
  }
  .card-chevron {
    grid-area: chevron;
    align-self: center;
  }
  .foot { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Site navigation">
  <div class="site-nav-inner">
    <a href="{{ domain }}/" class="site-nav-brand">
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#b08a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      State Licensing Reference
    </a>
    <div class="site-nav-links">
      <a href="{{ domain }}/" aria-current="page">All Specialties</a>
      <a href="#professions">Professions</a>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<header class="hero-wrapper">
  <h1>Travel Healthcare Licensing Hub</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Board-verified reciprocity, compact status, endorsement fees, and transfer timelines by profession.</p>

  <div class="stats-container">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-value">{{ deployed_count }}</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Professions</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-value">51</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Jurisdictions</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-value">400+</span>
      <span class="stat-label">State Guides</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="search-wrap">
  <div class="search-inner">
    <div class="search-field" role="search">
      <svg class="search-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="5"/><path d="M11 11L15 15"/></svg>
      <input id="professionSearch" class="search-input" type="text" placeholder="Search professions..." aria-label="Search professions" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false">
      <button class="search-clear" id="searchClear" aria-label="Clear search">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1 1L13 13M1 13L13 1"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<main class="content" id="professions">
  <p class="grid-title">Choose Your Profession</p>
  <div class="profession-grid" id="professionGrid">
    {% for card in cards %}
    <a class="profession-card" href="{{ card.url }}" data-profession="{{ card.title_full | lower }}" aria-label="Open {{ card.title_full }} licensing guides">
      <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">{{ card.icon | safe }}</span>
      <span class="card-body">
        <span class="card-title">{{ card.title_full }}</span>
        <span class="card-credential">{{ card.credential }}</span>
        <span class="card-exam">{{ card.exam }}</span>
      </span>
      <span class="compact-badge {{ card.badge.variant }}">{{ card.badge.label }}</span>
      <span class="card-chevron" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="8" height="13" viewBox="0 0 8 13" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1.5 1.5L6.5 6.5L1.5 11.5"/></svg>
      </span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="empty-state" id="emptyState" aria-live="polite">
    <h3>No Matches Found</h3>
    <p>Try adjusting your search term.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="features" id="about">
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h3>Board-Verified Data</h3>
      <p>Every fee, timeline, and requirement is sourced directly from official state boards.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h3>Real Processing Windows</h3>
      <p>See practical timeline ranges so you can plan contracts and start dates with less guesswork.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h3>Compact vs Endorsement Clarity</h3>
      <p>Quickly identify where compact privilege applies and where full endorsement is still required.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</main>

<div class="foot-wrapper">
  <footer class="foot">
    <div>
      <h2>About This Hub</h2>
      <p>State Licensing Reference is an independent resource for travel clinicians comparing licensing paths across the United States.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Professions</h2>
      <ul class="foot-links">
        {% for card in foot_cards %}
        <li><a href="{{ card.url }}">{{ card.title_plural }}</a></li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      <span class="foot-meta">Updated &bull; {{ today }}</span>
    </div>
  </footer>
</div>

<script>
const input = document.getElementById('professionSearch');
const clearBtn = document.getElementById('searchClear');
const cards = [...document.querySelectorAll('.profession-card')];
const grid = document.getElementById('professionGrid');
const emptyState = document.getElementById('emptyState');

function applyFilter() {
  const q = input.value.toLowerCase().trim();
  clearBtn.style.display = q ? 'flex' : 'none';
  let shown = 0;
  for (const card of cards) {
    const match = card.dataset.profession.includes(q);
    card.style.display = match ? '' : 'none';
    if (match) shown++;
  }
  grid.style.display = shown > 0 ? '' : 'none';
  emptyState.style.display = shown === 0 ? 'block' : 'none';
}

input.addEventListener('input', () => requestAnimationFrame(applyFilter));
clearBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
  input.value = '';
  input.focus();
  requestAnimationFrame(applyFilter);
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
